Metron Measurement & Control Materiel Technology has been a top supplier of vibration shakers, power amplifiers, modal analysis systems, slip tables, head-expanders and custom fixtures. We have achieved many remarkable honors and accreditations - for our systems are being implemented in fields of aerospace, aviation, weaponry, rail transportation, automobile manufacturing, medical devices, nuclear/wind/solar power generation and many others. 

We co-operate with a great number of top institutes including Shanghai JiaoTong University, TongJi University, SuZhou University, Northwestern Polytechnical University, Southern Illinois University and Saint Cloud State University. Our trustable team of experts ensure sound technological support in environmental and structural engineering, enabling us to accomplish the toughest requirements you demand.
